56:    * Whether the option is long or short.
57:    * <p>
58:    * At expiry, the long party will have the option to enter in this transaction; the short party will, at the option of
59:    * the long party, potentially enter into the inverse transaction.
60:    */
61:   @PropertyDefinition(validate = "notNull")
62:   private final LongShort longShort;
63:   /**
64:    * The expiry date of the option.
65:    * <p>
66:    * The option is European, and can only be exercised on the expiry date.
67:    */
